plyTime":"2019-06-16T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0fc6d4bd2b5840d1439579036c6cfab74f7df9","tid":1232583,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898ea42156fd2a656615f0616a118138094194b4","tid":1232583,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c8874eb76580a2a8a4eab7c774f95b5c4403d6","tid":1232583,"uid":157938,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=85bb16c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"508981afd23ce9fe794851911fab4bc08bcc49c7","tid":1232583,"uid":118520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38f317f4d17f15cf771c5cd7498232a730e6ef9","tid":1232583,"uid":40356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"YJ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b3562a66aeebaa79af8e74556baec363a490b5","tid":1232583,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbbb3c0b63c97dad7a815dfa33ffab0f7702c9a","tid":1232583,"uid":201649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:59:24.000Z","msg":"受教受教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595d44256b46db7cb1b59eb880a7614e02fda40b","tid":1232583,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"毅進制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81fe367d36d4bc6fccf946e917cec2a8521e8d2","tid":1232583,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ae47f0dc8373ae98c969969f1da6cbc529a36ad0","tid":1232583,"uid":92476,